name: OSIS
description: OSIS the utility token behind the education, tokenization, and exchange ecosystem that offers users the ability to launch their own NFTs & tokens. OSIS’ mission is to help all transition from Web2 to Web3 by simplifying access to the blockchain & ushering in a tokenized economy. The OSIS ecosystem includes everything you need to start your Web3 journey & take advantage of the tokenization revolution, such as: ✅OSIS Tokenizer (mint your own tokens & NFTs) ✅NFT Domains (in partnership with Unstoppable Domains) ✅OSIS Exchange (Decentralized Exchange) ✅CoinCare Digital Currency Cards (spend your digital currency anywhere)
